versions: 1.0.0: Basic editing features, simple tile selection and placement, 2 layers for objects and tiles, object placement, simple zoom and movement features. Import and export possibility
1.0.1: Bug fixes related to object deleting and object information display

1.2.0: New tile selection mode supporting previews supporting a complete visible list as well as a quick select tool, visual object listing, quick action features to rotate and move objects, manual hierarchy editing.
1.3.6: Full embed of the editor in the engine, saving functionalities, new map controls, bug fixes. Painting mode system.
